    O2["Output LlmAgent\nOpenClaw-aware"]
    CTX[("openclaw_ref ·\ntemplates · registry")]
    REQ[("setup requirements\n.md")]
    R2 <--> O2
    O2 <--> CTX
    O2 <--> REQ
  end

  I1 --> FMT
  FMT --> R2
  O2 -->|OPENCLAW_ENGINE_SETUP_GUIDE.md| FE

